eHive,is,an,online,collection,management,system,used,by,museums,galleries,and,other,collecting,organizations,to,manage,their,collections,The,service,allows,users,to,create,records,search,and,tag,content,and,publish,records,to,be,shared,online,The,eHive,API,allows,users,to,share,information,with,other,websites,applications,and,devices,The,API,is,RESTful,uses,OAuth,for,authentication,and,returns,responses,as,JSON,objects